 solar system from a narrow annulus of planetesimals,\nwhich reproduces their peculiar mass ratios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2016 20:00:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2016 15:55:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-19"}
