a significant part of parameter space for active galactic nuclei and\nnew-born pulsar models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Jul 2016 09:31:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2016 09:20:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 2 Apr 2018 06:35:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-03"}
